Ghaiwat et al. presents survey on different classification techniques that can be used for plant leaf disease classification.
Sanjay B et al. Authors in paper describe that there are mainly four steps in developed processing scheme, out of which, first one is, for the input RGB image.	
Mrunalini et al. presents the technique to classify and identify the different disease through which plants are affected.
Kulkarni et al. presents a methodology for early and accurately plant diseases detection, using artificial neural network (ANN) and diverse image processing techniques.
